  • 所有已实现的接口:
    Notifier<Experiment,Experiment.ExperimentMessage>, ValueStore, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class MultipleConfigurationExperiment
extends AbstractMultiConfExperiment
    Runs variations of a certain base experiment specified by a list of configurations. Each configuration is a map containing name/value pairs to describe the name of a property of baseExperiment which is set to a certain value.
    版本:
    "$Id$"
    作者:
    Robin Kreis, Torsten Hildebrandt, 2013-01-08
    另请参阅:
